2008-08-16

changed SGEFADE_FX_* and SGEFONT_FX_* to SGEFADEFX_* and SGEFONTFX_*

major api change on fade fx creation:
	SGEFADEFX *sgeFadeFXNew(Uint32 type, Uint32 runTime, SGESPRITE *source, SGESPRITE *destination);
	SGEFADEFX *sgeFadeFXNewSDLSurface(Uint32 type, Uint32 runTime, SDL_Surface *source, SDL_Surface *destination);

new function: void sgeFadeFXDeleteSurfaces(SGEFADEFX *fx, Uint8 yesno);

new fade effects + demo update:
	SGEFADEFX_SCROLL_LEFT,
	SGEFADEFX_SCROLL_RIGHT,
	SGEFADEFX_SCROLL_TOP,
	SGEFADEFX_SCROLL_BOTTOM

sgeFadeFXDeleteSprites() as alias for sgeFadeFXDeleteSurfaces()

2008-08-15

new functions:
	sgeCreateVideoSurface(int width, int height, int depth, Uint32 sdlflags); creates a sdl surface in video ram (if possible)
	sgeFontFXSetTarget(SGEFONTFX *fx, SDL_Surface *surface); change output target for fontfx

introducing fadeeffects + demo

effects:
	SGEFADE_FX_FADE,
	SGEFADE_FX_WIPE_LEFT,
	SGEFADE_FX_WIPE_RIGHT,
	SGEFADE_FX_WIPE_TOP,
	SGEFADE_FX_WIPE_BOTTOM

2008-08-14

font effect countdown was not blitting transparent
sgeFontFXHideOnPreDelay(fx, YES/NO); hides or displays the effect while in predelay phase

